N = int(input())
digit_sum = 0
while N>0:
    digit_sum += N%10
    N //= 10
print(digit_sum)


#et’s take 164 as input:

n % 10 → gives the last digit

164 % 10 = 4

Add it to digit_sum

digit_sum = 0 + 4 = 4

n // 10 → removes the last digit

164 // 10 = 16

Repeat the process:

16 % 10 = 6 → digit_sum = 4 + 6 = 10

16 // 10 = 1

1 % 10 = 1 → digit_sum = 10 + 1 = 11

Number becomes 0, loop stops.
